---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About">
  <article class="about-content">
    <h1 class="display-large">About Teardown Cafe</h1>
    
    <section class="about-section">
      <p class="lead-text">
        Welcome to Teardown Cafe, where curiosity meets coffee and every device 
        has a story to tell.
      </p>
      
      <h2 class="headline-large">What We Do</h2>
      <p>
        We meticulously disassemble and document consumer electronics, embedded systems, 
        and mechanical devices. Each teardown reveals the engineering decisions, component 
        choices, and design philosophies that make modern technology tick.
      </p>
      
      <h2 class="headline-large">Why Teardowns?</h2>
      <p>
        Understanding how devices work internally helps us appreciate the complexity 
        of modern engineering, make better purchasing decisions, and learn repair techniques. 
        Plus, it's just plain fascinating.
      </p>
      
      <h2 class="headline-large">Our Process</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Careful documentation with high-quality photography</li>
        <li>Component identification and analysis</li>
        <li>Build quality assessment</li>
        <li>Repairability evaluation</li>
        <li>Privacy-conscious metadata handling</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h2 class="headline-large">Privacy First</h2>
      <p>
        All uploaded images are automatically stripped of EXIF metadata, including 
        location data, to protect your privacy. We believe in responsible tech journalism.
      </p>
    </section>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  
  .about-content h1 {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  
  .lead-text {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--md-sys-color-on-surface-variant);
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  
  .about-section h2 {
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  .about-section p {
    margin: 1rem 0;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--md-sys-color-on-surface);
  }
  
  .about-section ul {
    margin: 1rem 0;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .about-section li {
    margin: 0.75rem 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--md-sys-color-on-surface);
  }
</style>
